WEBVTT


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.900
=Episode 30=

00:01:38.310 --> 00:01:39.240
Careful, Master Gu.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.670
I'm fine. Doing great.

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:42.000
Alright, you two get some rest.

00:01:44.190 --> 00:01:45.640
Come on, let me help you.

00:01:45.800 --> 00:01:46.910
Let's head back.

00:01:48.350 --> 00:01:49.190
What is it?

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:51.640
I don't want to go back.

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:52.830
I want to walk a bit.

00:01:53.230 --> 00:01:54.670
- I want to walk.
- We should go back.

00:01:54.670 --> 00:01:56.070
Let me walk a bit.

00:01:56.190 --> 00:01:57.920
Come on, let's go rest.

00:01:58.080 --> 00:01:58.950
You're drunk.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:00.160
Just a few steps.

00:02:00.550 --> 00:02:01.600
I don't want to go back.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:02.440
This old man...

00:02:03.070 --> 00:02:04.350
Has a home but won't go back.

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:05.440
What are you up to?

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.120
I feel great.

00:02:08.470 --> 00:02:09.710
Today is just great.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:12.320
Great drinks, and a great chat too.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:16.150
Been rehearsing Qinqiang opera lately.

00:02:16.430 --> 00:02:18.150
But we haven't really talked about it.

00:02:18.350 --> 00:02:19.390
Talking about it today...

00:02:20.740 --> 00:02:21.640
felt really good.

00:02:21.750 --> 00:02:23.600
Then hurry back and get some rest.

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:24.440
- Come on.
- I'm telling you...

00:02:25.030 --> 00:02:25.920
Now,

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:29.750
once Qin'e takes the stage in Chang'an

00:02:30.790 --> 00:02:32.350
and becomes a massive hit,

00:02:33.390 --> 00:02:34.600
I'll be out of here.

00:02:34.960 --> 00:02:35.960
Where will you go?

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:37.520
Who cares where?

00:02:38.030 --> 00:02:38.880
As long as I can

00:02:38.880 --> 00:02:41.230
release all this pent-up acting energy.

00:02:41.510 --> 00:02:44.400
Or the King of Hell will take it away.

00:02:45.350 --> 00:02:46.790
Master Gu, don't say that.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.920
You know how it is in the movies.

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.790
When someone says, "After this battle,

00:02:50.790 --> 00:02:52.040
I'll go home and get
married," or whatever.

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:53.430
Chances are, he won't survive.

00:02:54.710 --> 00:02:55.950
I don't fear death.

00:02:57.040 --> 00:02:59.710
I just fear living a half-life.

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:01.590
You won't die.

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:04.510
I'll be right there with you.

00:03:04.790 --> 00:03:06.640
We'll roam, perform, and stay together.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.710
For now, go get some sleep.

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:09.660
Let me walk you home.

00:03:09.670 --> 00:03:10.540
No need.

00:03:11.150 --> 00:03:12.310
Just leave now.

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:14.840
Let me get some peace and quiet.

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:16.870
Be alone for a bit?

00:03:19.350 --> 00:03:20.190
It's perfect.

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:23.400
Don't stay out too long.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.590
Mind the cold outside.

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:26.270
I'm off then.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.120
I'll leave you be.

00:03:28.230 --> 00:03:29.070
Leave me be.

00:03:30.350 --> 00:03:31.200
Leave me be.

00:03:34.350 --> 00:03:35.400
Go.

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:41.870
Aunt Hua, leave it there, I'll do it.

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:44.310
It's fine, think I'm really drunk?

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:45.430
Let me do it.

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.400
I'm just happy.

00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:52.120
These clothes look great.

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:53.150
Why don't you wear them?

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:56.870
They're not mine. Someone gave them to me.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.470
They're too expensive to throw away.

00:04:00.030 --> 00:04:01.560
I'll return them when I get the chance.

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:05.000
You have a boyfriend?

00:04:06.190 --> 00:04:07.150
He's not my boyfriend.

00:04:07.150 --> 00:04:08.190
I don't like him.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.560
Have someone you like?

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.200
No.

00:04:13.430 --> 00:04:14.270
I get it.

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:17.960
Can't be with the one you like.

00:04:19.710 --> 00:04:20.710
The one who likes you...

00:04:20.710 --> 00:04:22.190
You don't like him back.

00:04:22.470 --> 00:04:24.000
Isn't that just life?

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:26.190
Just like singing opera.

00:04:27.310 --> 00:04:28.680
No matter how high the pitch starts,

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:29.750
it's just the beginning.

00:04:31.710 --> 00:04:34.000
There's still a long way to go.

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:55.590
I...

00:04:56.750 --> 00:04:58.710
I finally found you.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:04.680
You...

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:26.360
Can't sleep?

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:32.560
What did your uncle say when he left?

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:34.870
Did he say

00:05:36.150 --> 00:05:37.710
that I should teach you how to sing?

00:05:39.630 --> 00:05:42.000
He said not to mention
Qinqiang opera to you.

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:45.120
He said you've been away for so long,

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:49.910
and it takes courage to pick it up again.

00:05:51.030 --> 00:05:52.270
He didn't want to upset you.

00:06:04.630 --> 00:06:05.480
Aunt Hua,

00:06:07.310 --> 00:06:08.950
since I joined the provincial troupe,

00:06:08.950 --> 00:06:10.680
I haven't had a single day of peace.

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:15.480
The provincial troupe's
diction is different.

00:06:16.630 --> 00:06:17.920
Everyone is anxious.

00:06:20.750 --> 00:06:22.070
I practice hard,

00:06:22.070 --> 00:06:23.600
but I can't see the way forward.

00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:26.920
Uncle tells me to focus on singing

00:06:27.270 --> 00:06:28.510
and not think too much.

00:06:31.390 --> 00:06:32.950
But the more he says,

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:35.040
the more confused I get.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:39.240
I rarely find peace of mind anymore.

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.510
Your uncle is right.

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:49.480
What they say or think

00:06:50.630 --> 00:06:51.630
doesn't matter.

00:06:52.870 --> 00:06:54.160
What matters is you.

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:57.040
But I have no idea.

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:02.310
I feel most at ease
when breathing the fire.

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:04.720
Because I promised my master

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:06.160
to surpass Wei Changsheng,

00:07:06.950 --> 00:07:08.800
and keep singing Qinqiang opera.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:27.510
It's grey.

00:07:32.630 --> 00:07:35.000
If he hadn't bumped into her that day,

00:07:35.190 --> 00:07:36.360
who knows how long Hua Caixiang

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.920
would have stayed in hiding.

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:40.430
She told Qin'e

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:43.190
she feels the way she is right now

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:45.750
isn't a good role model.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:51.190
Time really changes a person completely.

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:04.320
Laidi.

00:08:04.750 --> 00:08:05.680
Wake up.

00:08:07.070 --> 00:08:07.910
Wake up.

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.560
It's a great time for us.

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:13.430
We can't miss it.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:14.720
Come with me.

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:16.920
Where to?

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:23.720
Remember when you were little

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:25.310
and I took you to the valley

00:08:25.950 --> 00:08:26.920
to practice?

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.320
I remember.

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:32.510
That's our lucky place.

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:35.120
Let's warm up your voice first.

00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:41.750
Hu Sanyuan.

00:08:46.190 --> 00:08:49.430
Hu Sanyuan.

00:08:50.310 --> 00:08:53.920
Scumbag.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:58.630
Scumbag.

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:01.830
Bag... Bag...

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.630
Scumbag!

00:09:05.190 --> 00:09:08.430
Scumbag!

00:09:21.630 --> 00:09:22.920
Can't you stop smoking?

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:23.950
It's choking me.

00:09:24.510 --> 00:09:25.600
What else should I do?

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:27.390
Hope you choke!

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:28.840
I'll keep smoking.

00:09:29.830 --> 00:09:31.120
I wish I were dead anyway.

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.120
If I die,

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.510
let's see what you'll eat.

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:35.480
Don't worry.

00:09:35.950 --> 00:09:37.190
I'll starve if you die.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:43.000
Other guys are fixing up their houses

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.000
or tinkering with something.

00:09:44.430 --> 00:09:46.160
You can't even fix a broken board.

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:47.030
Yet all day long,

00:09:47.030 --> 00:09:48.000
you act all tough

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.000
for nothing!

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.560
Leave if you don't like it.

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:51.430
Now? Why didn't you

00:09:51.430 --> 00:09:52.510
say so earlier?

00:09:52.510 --> 00:09:53.430
You got someone new,

00:09:53.430 --> 00:09:54.480
so I'm in the way now?

00:09:55.590 --> 00:09:56.430
What are you doing?

00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:57.270
To make room?

00:09:57.280 --> 00:09:58.560
Looking for someone. What?

00:09:59.190 --> 00:10:00.360
Who are you looking for?

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:02.880
- Look at you.
- Does Pi Liang live here?

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:04.840
Pi Liang?

00:10:04.840 --> 00:10:06.000
- I won't leave!
- Don't know him.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:06.960
I'll just annoy you.

00:10:07.510 --> 00:10:08.600
What kind of life is this?

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.670
You think I'm having a good life?

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:15.270
Why didn't you say that earlier?

00:10:19.030 --> 00:10:19.870
Master.

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:21.320
I bought breakfast.

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:22.550
What are you eating?

00:10:22.670 --> 00:10:23.720
Your master hasn't eaten yet.

00:11:46.510 --> 00:11:48.360
They threw money in a drum bag?

00:11:48.870 --> 00:11:50.750
They really took us for buskers.

00:11:51.550 --> 00:11:53.200
Nine, ten.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:57.550
Two yuan and forty-eight fen!

00:11:58.790 --> 00:12:00.390
Thirty days in a month.

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:03.480
We could make two yuan a day.

00:12:03.630 --> 00:12:05.030
That's sixty yuan a month!

00:12:05.030 --> 00:12:06.150
That's not bad.

00:12:06.630 --> 00:12:07.840
Don't beat people's backs.

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:09.440
Just beat the drum for a living.

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:12.150
One tree doesn't make a forest.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:14.960
My drumming is only worth fifty fen.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:16.870
The rest is for you and Qin'e's singing.

00:12:17.750 --> 00:12:18.750
Now we don't need to.

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.480
Maybe we can make a living off it later.

00:12:22.150 --> 00:12:23.320
When is later?

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.440
It's up to you.

00:12:24.750 --> 00:12:25.960
Just give the word.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:27.840
I'll pedal my trike and take you anywhere.

00:12:32.780 --> 00:12:36.060
(Ye Ma Ma)

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:38.600
They say this movie is really good.

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.240
Wanna watch it?

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:43.960
No.

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:46.910
A ticket is one yuan and twenty fen.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:49.120
The money in that bag is just enough.

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:50.270
Maybe it's meant to be.

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:51.440
Watch it.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:59.440
The last time we saw a movie together

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:01.440
was back in the opera troupe.

00:13:01.550 --> 00:13:03.120
We were rehearsing Hong Hu Chi Wei Dui.

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:05.270
They played an outdoor movie, remember?

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:11.240
It feels like it was just yesterday.

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.260
I kept asking you

00:13:13.270 --> 00:13:14.390
what was in that letter,

00:13:14.390 --> 00:13:15.600
but you just wouldn't tell me.

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:17.440
I was so mad.

00:13:20.990 --> 00:13:21.840
Tell me, back then,

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:24.550
if that letter hadn't gotten soaked,

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:27.080
would things between us

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:28.910
have been different?

00:13:31.870 --> 00:13:32.910
Just watch the movie.

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.630
We paid for the tickets.

00:13:42.480 --> 00:13:49.600
♪Tell Huiniang not to be so sad♪

00:13:55.630 --> 00:14:02.550
♪Listen and take my words to heart♪

00:14:05.340 --> 00:14:06.200
What's wrong?

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:10.270
♪Goddess of the Ninth Heavens pities you♪

00:14:11.790 --> 00:14:13.240
Wanna know what I wrote

00:14:13.910 --> 00:14:15.200
in that letter, right?

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:20.360
I'll tell you.

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:23.480
I just wrote three words.

00:14:25.270 --> 00:14:26.110
"Take me in."

00:14:26.550 --> 00:14:27.710
They cut ties with me.

00:14:29.870 --> 00:14:31.320
But I wrote it thirty times.

00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:33.510
What did you say?

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:40.150
Look, Tubagou is coming down!

00:14:41.790 --> 00:14:43.240
Tubagou is coming down!

00:14:45.270 --> 00:14:51.750
Tubagou is coming down!

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.440
Everyone, look closely!

00:14:53.630 --> 00:14:55.720
Gu Cunxiao, director of
the provincial troupe,

00:14:55.750 --> 00:14:58.000
was a total thug in the old society!

00:14:58.670 --> 00:15:00.120
My mom is his lawful wife.

00:15:00.150 --> 00:15:02.720
Yet he took an opera
performer as his mistress.

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:04.390
(Old thug Gu Cunxiao)
Then came Liberation.

00:15:04.670 --> 00:15:06.630
(Give my mother dignity)
He feared the People's Government.

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:09.270
So he ran off with that mistress.

00:15:09.270 --> 00:15:10.670
He abandoned my mom.

00:15:11.150 --> 00:15:13.000
Now Reform is here.

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:14.910
He wants to take my mom away.

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:17.150
He treats her like his private property

00:15:17.320 --> 00:15:18.320
and his servant

00:15:18.360 --> 00:15:20.480
who works herself to the bone!

00:15:20.910 --> 00:15:22.080
Young man,

00:15:22.150 --> 00:15:24.270
she's still your mother.

00:15:24.270 --> 00:15:25.510
How can you say that?

00:15:25.510 --> 00:15:26.360
I don't care.

00:15:26.370 --> 00:15:27.270
The provincial troupe

00:15:27.270 --> 00:15:28.510
must give me an explanation today.

00:15:30.510 --> 00:15:32.480
How can the provincial troupe explain it?

00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:33.840
If you have an issue,

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:35.630
go to the police station.

00:15:35.630 --> 00:15:36.470
Right?

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:37.600
You can't act like this here.

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:39.390
You're personally attacking him.

00:15:39.750 --> 00:15:41.550
- That's illegal!
- Exactly.

00:15:41.550 --> 00:15:43.000
What attack? Stop your nonsense!

00:15:43.870 --> 00:15:45.360
He's one of your guys.

00:15:45.480 --> 00:15:46.750
Of course, you'd cover for him.

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:47.840
I don't care.

00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:50.150
You have to give my mom back today!

00:15:50.390 --> 00:15:52.480
Oh, and you need to pay me.

00:15:52.600 --> 00:15:53.550
For my emotional distress!

00:15:53.550 --> 00:15:54.960
Pay you? Not a chance!

00:15:56.270 --> 00:15:58.030
Can you take this banner down first?

00:15:58.030 --> 00:15:58.870
What money?

00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:00.120
Master Gu abandoned his family?

00:16:00.120 --> 00:16:01.870
He dumped his wife and kid?

00:16:02.390 --> 00:16:03.230
Master Chen.

00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:05.480
Master Chen, who are you calling?

00:16:06.030 --> 00:16:06.870
Calling the police.

00:16:06.880 --> 00:16:08.480
Why call the police? Hang up!

00:16:08.960 --> 00:16:09.960
Hang up now!

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:12.320
Think things aren't bad enough?

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:13.630
Calling the police?

00:16:13.670 --> 00:16:16.510
We need to learn to protect our own.

00:16:16.510 --> 00:16:17.840
I said I'd call the police.

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:19.360
That was just to scare him.

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:22.750
Let's see how long he keeps it up.

00:16:23.390 --> 00:16:24.840
I demand an explanation!

00:16:25.740 --> 00:16:26.630
An explanation!

00:16:26.630 --> 00:16:27.470
He's causing trouble!

00:16:27.790 --> 00:16:29.360
Stop banging on the door!

00:16:29.390 --> 00:16:30.510
You break it, you pay for it!

00:16:30.750 --> 00:16:31.840
Stop making a scene!

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:33.630
Buddy, buddy, buddy!

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:36.200
Don't act up at the
provincial troupe's door.

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.910
You're blocking the whole entrance.

00:16:37.910 --> 00:16:39.750
This is illegal, you know?

00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.110
Who are you?

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:43.270
Who are you?

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:44.440
What?

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:47.150
I've heard your story.

00:16:47.440 --> 00:16:49.870
Your mom didn't divorce Gu Cunxiao.

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:53.240
How did your dad have you?

00:16:55.910 --> 00:16:56.910
I was just saying.

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:58.320
He abandoned my mom.

00:16:58.960 --> 00:17:00.000
My dad felt sorry for her.

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.150
So he took her in.

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:02.360
That's how I was born.

00:17:06.200 --> 00:17:08.670
So your mom didn't divorce Gu Cunxiao.

00:17:09.790 --> 00:17:11.390
Then your mom and dad are

00:17:11.390 --> 00:17:12.240
living together unlawfully.

00:17:12.600 --> 00:17:13.750
Right, right.

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:14.600
Exactly.

00:17:14.600 --> 00:17:16.360
That is unlawful, you know?

00:17:16.360 --> 00:17:18.120
They could go to jail for it!

00:17:18.200 --> 00:17:21.240
Your very birth is unlawful!

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:24.120
So, what's going on?

00:17:24.600 --> 00:17:25.440
Who did you say?

00:17:25.750 --> 00:17:26.590
I'll hit you!

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:32.910
I didn't hit him!

00:17:34.270 --> 00:17:35.110
I didn't touch him!

00:17:35.240 --> 00:17:36.080
I didn't!

00:17:37.550 --> 00:17:39.000
Stop him! Don't let him get away!

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:40.600
- Call the police, quick!
- Call the police!

00:17:40.630 --> 00:17:42.080
This is illegal! He hit people!

00:17:43.870 --> 00:17:44.910
Stop him! Stop him!

00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:46.160
- Liu Hongbing!
- Don't let him escape!

00:17:46.360 --> 00:17:47.360
He ran off.

00:17:47.750 --> 00:17:48.670
He ran off!

00:17:48.870 --> 00:17:49.720
He ran off.

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:50.680
Are you okay?

00:17:52.030 --> 00:17:53.600
I already called the police!

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:54.550
How was my acting?

00:17:55.670 --> 00:17:56.750
Could I be an actor?

00:17:57.870 --> 00:17:58.710
Young man.

00:17:59.750 --> 00:18:00.590
Young man.

00:18:01.000 --> 00:18:01.840
Thank you.

00:18:02.270 --> 00:18:03.110
No big deal.

00:18:03.790 --> 00:18:04.630
What's your name?

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:06.200
I'm Liu Hongbing.

00:18:06.510 --> 00:18:07.350
Thank you.

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:09.390
Where are you from?

00:18:10.390 --> 00:18:11.240
- Liu Hongbing!
- Yi Qin'e...

00:18:11.910 --> 00:18:13.080
I'm her boyfriend.

00:18:17.120 --> 00:18:18.550
Qin'e! Qin'e! Qin'e!

00:18:18.550 --> 00:18:19.440
Then you're one of us!

00:18:19.580 --> 00:18:20.430
One of us!

00:18:20.440 --> 00:18:22.200
Come in, come in!

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:23.040
Qin'e!

00:18:23.050 --> 00:18:24.030
Come on in!

00:18:24.030 --> 00:18:24.870
Come in!

00:18:26.150 --> 00:18:27.080
Comrade Gu Cunxiao,

00:18:28.080 --> 00:18:28.920
what is going on here?

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:31.600
About our policy,

00:18:32.390 --> 00:18:33.480
you should know it well, right?

00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:34.440
I do know it.

00:18:35.480 --> 00:18:36.960
Confess for leniency, resist for severity.

00:18:37.510 --> 00:18:38.350
No,

00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:40.030
it's about monogamy!

00:18:41.720 --> 00:18:43.440
How could a mistake from Pre-Liberation

00:18:43.720 --> 00:18:45.310
be repeated Post-Liberation?

00:18:48.310 --> 00:18:49.590
I'm more wronged than Dou E.

00:18:51.160 --> 00:18:52.550
I didn't take her back.

00:18:53.270 --> 00:18:55.070
She found her way back on her own.

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:57.720
Our show became a hit in Beishan.

00:18:58.160 --> 00:19:00.440
She came back on her own.

00:19:01.180 --> 00:19:02.540
You already said that.

00:19:03.220 --> 00:19:04.340
What about her?

00:19:05.060 --> 00:19:05.900
Where did she come from?

00:19:06.460 --> 00:19:07.300
Calm down.

00:19:08.180 --> 00:19:09.020
Take your time.

00:19:11.260 --> 00:19:12.100
Let's talk outside.

00:19:14.820 --> 00:19:16.540
Chief Qiao, come here.

00:19:22.100 --> 00:19:23.980
The older one is Zhang Su'e.

00:19:24.540 --> 00:19:26.020
Someone told her I was here.

00:19:26.020 --> 00:19:27.740
She found me a few days ago.

00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:30.940
We never officially divorced.

00:19:31.900 --> 00:19:33.300
I had no choice back then.

00:19:34.180 --> 00:19:36.140
I hustled every day to make ends meet.

00:19:36.300 --> 00:19:38.820
Life was stifling and miserable.

00:19:38.820 --> 00:19:40.060
I was constantly picked on.

00:19:40.500 --> 00:19:42.540
My situation was even worse.

00:19:42.820 --> 00:19:44.780
She suffered a lot with me.

00:19:45.220 --> 00:19:47.100
She ran into a local boss who

00:19:48.300 --> 00:19:49.180
took a fancy to her.

00:19:50.100 --> 00:19:51.500
If she hadn't given in,

00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:54.060
I'd probably be dead.

00:19:54.860 --> 00:19:56.740
That man is dead now.

00:19:57.540 --> 00:19:59.380
His son is even worse.

00:19:59.660 --> 00:20:01.740
He treats her like a pack animal,

00:20:02.500 --> 00:20:03.700
always beating and cursing her.

00:20:04.220 --> 00:20:05.820
She couldn't take it anymore.

00:20:05.900 --> 00:20:06.740
So she ran away

00:20:06.940 --> 00:20:07.780
and found me.

00:20:08.140 --> 00:20:10.620
She was a salt merchant's daughter.

00:20:11.620 --> 00:20:12.900
She saw my play

00:20:13.220 --> 00:20:14.700
and eloped with me.

00:20:16.380 --> 00:20:18.460
We were a couple after all.

00:20:18.900 --> 00:20:20.260
She's in such a state,

00:20:20.260 --> 00:20:21.260
and she finds me.

00:20:21.300 --> 00:20:22.540
Sent her away?

00:20:23.140 --> 00:20:24.020
I can't

00:20:24.060 --> 00:20:25.580
do that to her.

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:26.540
She stays,

00:20:26.700 --> 00:20:27.580
and here you are.

00:20:29.260 --> 00:20:32.180
Even a hero cannot overcome
the trial of a beauty.

00:20:33.860 --> 00:20:34.700
Chief Qiao,

00:20:35.420 --> 00:20:37.340
Gu didn't do it on purpose.

00:20:38.300 --> 00:20:40.580
This isn't illegal, right?

00:20:41.220 --> 00:20:42.060
Here's the thing.

00:20:43.620 --> 00:20:45.180
From a legal perspective,

00:20:45.580 --> 00:20:46.700
it's not illegal yet.

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:48.220
- Good.
- But look.

00:20:48.220 --> 00:20:49.060
Good.

00:20:52.100 --> 00:20:53.700
This living arrangement of you three,

00:20:53.980 --> 00:20:55.540
if it continues like this,

00:20:55.780 --> 00:20:57.060
you'll be committing bigamy.

00:20:57.580 --> 00:20:58.580
Separate immediately.

00:20:58.700 --> 00:20:59.940
Not just immediately,

00:21:00.020 --> 00:21:01.260
you must separate completely.

00:21:01.540 --> 00:21:02.500
Completely.

00:21:02.820 --> 00:21:03.780
Moving to a new place

00:21:03.780 --> 00:21:04.980
won't solve the problem.

00:21:05.380 --> 00:21:06.740
One of them has to leave.

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:09.180
Relax, it'll be fine.

00:21:09.560 --> 00:21:10.440
No big deal.

00:21:10.450 --> 00:21:11.580
Who would've thought?

00:21:11.820 --> 00:21:13.380
Gu is quite something.

00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:14.620
He has two wives.

00:21:15.100 --> 00:21:16.340
At his age,

00:21:16.700 --> 00:21:18.300
he has no shame at all.

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:21.500
What are you saying?

00:21:22.260 --> 00:21:23.660
We're all men. Stop pretending.

00:21:24.420 --> 00:21:25.300
Who are you?

00:21:25.900 --> 00:21:26.740
Family.

00:21:27.300 --> 00:21:28.140
And you?

00:21:28.180 --> 00:21:29.380
The troupe's sound engineer.

00:21:29.380 --> 00:21:30.220
Got a problem?

00:21:30.780 --> 00:21:32.540
Just keep quiet.

00:21:37.420 --> 00:21:39.420
I just despise unfaithful men.

00:21:40.620 --> 00:21:41.980
Though he is your master,

00:21:41.980 --> 00:21:42.860
regarding this matter,

00:21:42.860 --> 00:21:43.980
I still look down on him.

00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:46.060
Unlike me,

00:21:46.940 --> 00:21:47.820
in this lifetime,

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:49.460
having just you is enough.

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:54.220
If, after a week,

00:21:54.580 --> 00:21:56.140
we still get public complaints,

00:21:56.140 --> 00:21:57.420
we won't go easy on you.

00:21:57.620 --> 00:21:59.580
Turn back before it's too late.

00:21:59.980 --> 00:22:02.740
Stubbornness leads to endless pain.

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:04.460
- Gu.
- Let's go.

00:22:04.580 --> 00:22:05.580
Resolve it quickly.

00:22:07.220 --> 00:22:09.740
Chief Qiao, you're well-informed.

00:22:10.020 --> 00:22:12.100
You found out after just one week.

00:22:12.700 --> 00:22:13.540
So what?

00:22:13.860 --> 00:22:15.900
It proves the public is sharp.

00:22:15.900 --> 00:22:16.740
Right, right.

00:22:17.220 --> 00:22:18.620
Which citizen was it?

00:22:18.620 --> 00:22:20.620
Tell me so I can praise him or her.

00:22:21.060 --> 00:22:23.500
Your group has to sort out

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:25.540
Comrade Gu Cunxiao's issue quickly.

00:22:26.940 --> 00:22:27.780
Okay.

00:22:27.790 --> 00:22:29.780
- That's it, I'm off.
- Okay, okay.

00:22:32.300 --> 00:22:33.540
Qin'e. Qin'e.

00:22:33.960 --> 00:22:34.820
Check on Gu.

00:22:34.820 --> 00:22:36.180
Let me know if anything happens.

00:22:37.060 --> 00:22:38.540
Troupe Leader Shan, I've got this.

00:22:38.540 --> 00:22:39.860
- Okay, go ahead.
- The police...

00:22:39.860 --> 00:22:40.700
Go ahead.

00:22:45.380 --> 00:22:47.220
Look at all the men in this troupe.

00:22:47.220 --> 00:22:49.060
You're less capable
than one family member.

00:22:50.260 --> 00:22:51.540
Break it up. Go.

00:22:52.340 --> 00:22:53.180
Liu Jinsong.

00:22:54.020 --> 00:22:56.500
You play dumb when work is assigned,

00:22:56.620 --> 00:22:58.300
but you're first in line for drama.

00:22:58.540 --> 00:22:59.660
Dear Troupe Leader.

00:22:59.660 --> 00:23:00.980
You completely wronged me.

00:23:00.980 --> 00:23:02.620
I was rehearsing perfectly fine.

00:23:02.620 --> 00:23:03.740
Then Pi Liang yelled

00:23:03.740 --> 00:23:04.700
and called us all over here.

00:23:04.700 --> 00:23:05.740
It's true, right?

00:23:05.780 --> 00:23:07.420
Liu Jinsong, don't talk nonsense.

00:23:07.700 --> 00:23:09.460
What do you mean you heard me yell?

00:23:09.460 --> 00:23:10.820
I heard someone else yelling too.

00:23:10.820 --> 00:23:12.260
I only heard you yell.

00:23:12.460 --> 00:23:14.020
Say that again, and I'll
rip your mouth off.

00:23:14.020 --> 00:23:14.860
Bring it on.

00:23:19.380 --> 00:23:20.220
Why are you looking at me?

00:23:20.580 --> 00:23:21.860
Because you're pretty.

00:23:22.140 --> 00:23:23.420
Who else would I look at?

00:23:24.300 --> 00:23:25.980
About fighting for the lead role,

00:23:26.020 --> 00:23:27.460
I think it's completely normal.

00:23:28.420 --> 00:23:30.940
But you need to do it the right way.

00:23:31.140 --> 00:23:32.980
You can't use such dirty tricks.

00:23:33.820 --> 00:23:36.220
Alright, that's enough. Break it up.

00:23:37.140 --> 00:23:37.980
Master.

00:23:57.260 --> 00:23:59.140
Go call your master in.

00:23:59.220 --> 00:24:00.340
Don't stand out there.

00:24:01.340 --> 00:24:02.680
The issue needs to be resolved.

00:24:04.100 --> 00:24:05.420
- Why are you staring?
- We need an answer.

00:24:05.420 --> 00:24:06.620
Go, go.

00:24:07.900 --> 00:24:09.020
Just go!

00:24:12.540 --> 00:24:14.020
I'd better go back.

00:24:15.860 --> 00:24:17.900
I don't want to burden your master.

00:24:19.660 --> 00:24:20.540
That home...

00:24:21.660 --> 00:24:24.700
I couldn't stay there for another minute.

00:24:26.660 --> 00:24:27.540
Ma'am...

00:24:28.420 --> 00:24:30.500
if I had any other choice,

00:24:31.780 --> 00:24:34.100
I wouldn't have come here.

00:24:34.700 --> 00:24:35.540
Right, right!

00:24:36.380 --> 00:24:37.820
I'm the one who should leave.

00:24:38.420 --> 00:24:39.900
I was cast aside.

00:24:40.060 --> 00:24:42.380
I'll go back to the country and starve.

00:24:42.900 --> 00:24:45.340
Ma'am, what are you saying?

00:24:45.620 --> 00:24:46.460
What am I saying?

00:24:46.620 --> 00:24:47.660
The honest truth.

00:24:48.220 --> 00:24:49.780
At least she has a son.

00:24:49.780 --> 00:24:51.500
Good or bad, she's still alive.

00:24:51.860 --> 00:24:52.700
Master, why squatting here?

00:24:52.700 --> 00:24:53.740
What do I have?

00:24:53.740 --> 00:24:54.700
I'd just starve.

00:24:54.700 --> 00:24:55.660
Why are you here?

00:24:56.060 --> 00:24:56.920
What's in your hand?

00:24:56.940 --> 00:24:58.300
Food for Master.

00:24:58.660 --> 00:24:59.740
What are you waiting for?

00:25:00.300 --> 00:25:01.460
They need to eat.

00:25:01.460 --> 00:25:02.380
Hurry up and serve it.

00:25:03.340 --> 00:25:04.260
Quick, quick!

00:25:04.260 --> 00:25:06.580
Oh my heavens!

00:25:06.580 --> 00:25:08.340
Look at the time!

00:25:08.940 --> 00:25:10.300
You're not watching the show?

00:25:12.900 --> 00:25:14.220
You don't care at all?

00:25:14.220 --> 00:25:15.060
It started?

00:25:16.340 --> 00:25:18.060
What time is it? When did it start?

00:25:20.380 --> 00:25:21.260
Ma'am.

00:25:22.140 --> 00:25:23.420
What's the big deal?

00:25:24.180 --> 00:25:25.020
Ma'am.

00:25:25.220 --> 00:25:26.220
Ma'am, have some food.

00:25:26.220 --> 00:25:27.060
Here.

00:25:27.260 --> 00:25:28.300
They were fine yesterday.

00:25:28.300 --> 00:25:29.900
Why are they arguing today?

00:25:30.380 --> 00:25:31.580
How can they be together?

00:25:32.260 --> 00:25:33.820
She always picks fights with him,

00:25:33.860 --> 00:25:34.700
doing nothing else.

00:25:34.700 --> 00:25:35.780
Just sitting on the bed smoking.

00:25:36.500 --> 00:25:39.060
Look, even the actress quit smoking.

00:25:39.300 --> 00:25:40.220
Why are you still smoking?

00:25:41.530 --> 00:25:42.420
Right?

00:25:42.440 --> 00:25:43.300
Go that way.

00:25:43.300 --> 00:25:44.380
Shun! Shun!

00:25:45.300 --> 00:25:46.140
Come here.

00:25:46.340 --> 00:25:47.220
Director, what is it?

00:25:47.260 --> 00:25:49.220
What's with this lighting?

00:25:49.220 --> 00:25:50.100
It's way too bright.

00:25:50.100 --> 00:25:51.580
Does this look like West Lake?

00:25:51.580 --> 00:25:52.420
But...

00:25:52.580 --> 00:25:54.740
You said they need to see the acting.

00:25:54.740 --> 00:25:56.660
The atmosphere doesn't matter.

00:25:57.100 --> 00:25:58.420
Are you the director, or am I?

00:25:58.640 --> 00:25:59.500
You're the director.

00:25:59.500 --> 00:26:00.420
What do we do then?

00:26:01.020 --> 00:26:03.420
I want a West Lake vibe.

00:26:03.420 --> 00:26:04.540
That's your duty.

00:26:04.540 --> 00:26:05.380
You're asking me?

00:26:05.500 --> 00:26:06.620
Alright, I'll tweak it.

00:26:06.620 --> 00:26:07.820
I'll tweak it.

00:26:08.300 --> 00:26:10.020
Come on, make it a bit darker.

00:26:10.300 --> 00:26:13.700
Bringing West Lake's beauty to the stage?

00:26:13.700 --> 00:26:14.540
Director Feng.

00:26:17.380 --> 00:26:19.100
We'll add some lights later.

00:26:19.820 --> 00:26:20.940
And put on some music.

00:26:21.860 --> 00:26:22.700
Perfect.

00:26:24.700 --> 00:26:25.660
It's getting late.

00:26:25.820 --> 00:26:27.460
Any advice for me, Director Gu?

00:26:28.660 --> 00:26:29.620
You're right.

00:26:31.140 --> 00:26:33.260
Only tables, chairs, and curtains.

00:26:33.940 --> 00:26:35.140
It really is outdated.

00:26:35.700 --> 00:26:37.140
Take your time enjoying it.

00:26:37.140 --> 00:26:38.580
I'm heading home for dinner.

00:26:57.340 --> 00:26:58.700
I'm leaving.

00:27:01.900 --> 00:27:02.740
Where are you going?

00:27:03.660 --> 00:27:04.540
I'm leaving here.

00:27:06.380 --> 00:27:07.380
Where I used to go

00:27:08.100 --> 00:27:09.140
is where I'm going now.

00:27:10.940 --> 00:27:11.780
Then

00:27:12.660 --> 00:27:14.420
what about your two wives?

00:27:16.900 --> 00:27:17.820
I will

00:27:18.340 --> 00:27:20.420
give them all my savings.

00:27:21.540 --> 00:27:22.860
The Troupe Leader agreed

00:27:23.340 --> 00:27:25.340
to let them stay in that house.

00:27:25.900 --> 00:27:26.820
Once I'm gone,

00:27:27.540 --> 00:27:29.060
they'll stop fighting.

00:27:29.300 --> 00:27:30.140
But...

00:27:30.740 --> 00:27:31.580
Don't worry.

00:27:32.660 --> 00:27:36.580
People can survive without each other.

00:27:37.740 --> 00:27:39.700
My only worry right now

00:27:39.980 --> 00:27:40.900
is you.

00:27:42.260 --> 00:27:44.420
I brought you here from Ningzhou.

00:27:45.620 --> 00:27:47.100
But I made you suffer here.

00:27:47.860 --> 00:27:48.740
This injustice...

00:27:49.900 --> 00:27:51.380
I've also kept it to myself.

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:54.780
But...

00:27:55.700 --> 00:27:56.980
after everything recently,

00:27:57.780 --> 00:27:59.580
especially after that
stand double incident,

00:28:00.220 --> 00:28:01.060
I realized

00:28:03.220 --> 00:28:04.380
you're stronger than I thought.

00:28:05.220 --> 00:28:07.460
Even stronger than me.

00:28:09.620 --> 00:28:10.460
Master Gu,

00:28:11.460 --> 00:28:12.980
please don't comfort me.

00:28:12.980 --> 00:28:14.540
I'm not. It's the truth.

00:28:15.060 --> 00:28:16.460
You're very grounded.

00:28:17.300 --> 00:28:18.660
Because your mind is clear.

00:28:19.860 --> 00:28:21.580
You don't try to control life.

00:28:21.860 --> 00:28:23.940
That's why you can survive in the cracks

00:28:23.940 --> 00:28:25.020
of life.

00:28:25.780 --> 00:28:27.180
Kid, remember this.

00:28:27.660 --> 00:28:30.380
Always stay like this.

00:28:30.860 --> 00:28:31.700
Don't change.

00:28:32.700 --> 00:28:33.860
I don't understand.

00:28:36.140 --> 00:28:38.220
What does singing opera mean to you?

00:28:40.300 --> 00:28:41.380
I never thought about it.

00:28:41.820 --> 00:28:42.820
Exactly.

00:28:43.660 --> 00:28:45.260
It's like many things in life.

00:28:45.260 --> 00:28:47.700
The more you think,
the less it makes sense.

00:28:50.020 --> 00:28:51.060
Just remember,

00:28:51.380 --> 00:28:52.740
life is long,

00:28:53.820 --> 00:28:55.260
and it's not just about opera.

00:28:56.020 --> 00:28:59.060
If you can still sing, do it well.

00:28:59.510 --> 00:29:00.510
If you can't sing anymore,

00:29:02.240 --> 00:29:03.460
just live your life well.

00:29:07.620 --> 00:29:08.460
I'll remember it.

00:29:55.060 --> 00:29:58.940
♪Just do good deeds♪

00:29:59.820 --> 00:30:03.220
♪And don't ask♪

00:30:04.340 --> 00:30:09.580
♪About the future♪

00:30:19.540 --> 00:30:21.300
Gu Cunxiao's family matter

00:30:21.420 --> 00:30:23.620
is a mess left by history.

00:30:24.300 --> 00:30:25.940
He left the troupe

00:30:25.940 --> 00:30:27.980
not to hide from his past affairs.

00:30:28.980 --> 00:30:31.500
His vision for Qinqiang opera clashed

00:30:31.620 --> 00:30:32.980
with Director Feng's.

00:30:34.020 --> 00:30:36.900
But learning a bit from Director Feng

00:30:37.380 --> 00:30:40.620
helped him realize what he wants to sing.

00:30:41.460 --> 00:30:43.980
He needs to hurry up and sing.

00:30:56.140 --> 00:30:57.660
He said he needed the bathroom.

00:30:58.540 --> 00:30:59.740
But once he left,

00:31:01.120 --> 00:31:02.720
he never came back.

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:05.940
Break it up! It's early, get to work.

00:31:06.660 --> 00:31:09.340
Gu really left?

00:31:10.660 --> 00:31:13.420
He didn't take any valuables with him.

00:31:14.020 --> 00:31:14.860
Alright.

00:31:15.060 --> 00:31:15.940
With him gone,

00:31:16.260 --> 00:31:17.820
the problem is pretty much solved.

00:31:18.740 --> 00:31:19.820
Nothing left to investigate.

00:31:21.940 --> 00:31:26.220
You two ladies go back inside and rest.

00:31:27.060 --> 00:31:27.980
Sir, sir!

00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:29.380
You can't just leave.

00:31:29.460 --> 00:31:32.020
How are we two old women supposed to live?

00:31:32.020 --> 00:31:33.620
You officials can't just ignore us.

00:31:33.820 --> 00:31:34.660
Well...

00:31:35.140 --> 00:31:36.820
Just keep living in this house for now.

00:31:37.260 --> 00:31:38.820
If you run into trouble,

00:31:38.820 --> 00:31:40.180
tell the neighborhood committee.

00:31:40.380 --> 00:31:42.060
We'll work it out together.

00:31:42.260 --> 00:31:43.860
If there are still issues,

00:31:43.860 --> 00:31:44.700
Chief Qiao,

00:31:45.020 --> 00:31:46.420
please help sort them out.

00:31:46.420 --> 00:31:47.260
Right.

00:31:47.620 --> 00:31:49.180
Go in and rest.

00:31:58.340 --> 00:31:59.180
Come on.

00:32:00.340 --> 00:32:01.260
Go back inside.

00:32:01.740 --> 00:32:02.700
I'll reheat the food.

00:32:06.300 --> 00:32:07.500
He left just like that?

00:32:10.060 --> 00:32:10.900
What's wrong?

00:32:11.420 --> 00:32:12.740
You even got attached?

00:32:12.780 --> 00:32:14.260
Now that he's gone, you're off?

00:32:15.340 --> 00:32:17.300
It's just a difference in views.

00:32:17.460 --> 00:32:19.580
I have nothing against him.

00:32:20.020 --> 00:32:21.060
I know that.

00:32:21.380 --> 00:32:23.060
Don't overthink it now.

00:32:23.220 --> 00:32:24.500
Just focus on rehearsal.

00:32:25.540 --> 00:32:27.540
Right, I'll just focus on rehearsal.

00:32:27.580 --> 00:32:29.260
Consider it fulfilling his wish.

00:32:29.860 --> 00:32:30.980
I'll leave it to you.

00:32:32.460 --> 00:32:33.300
Do a good job.

00:32:44.820 --> 00:32:46.300
Okay, spotlight.

00:32:47.980 --> 00:32:49.500
Fade out.

00:32:49.900 --> 00:32:50.940
Lili, off.

00:32:51.260 --> 00:32:52.100
Qin'e, on.

00:32:52.580 --> 00:32:53.420
Okay.

00:32:54.620 --> 00:32:56.620
Okay, lights up.

00:32:56.860 --> 00:32:57.700
Stand steady.

00:32:58.820 --> 00:32:59.660
Okay.

00:33:06.500 --> 00:33:07.460
Well,

00:33:07.460 --> 00:33:09.740
about your current singing style...

00:33:11.900 --> 00:33:14.340
You need a bit more emotion.

00:33:14.340 --> 00:33:16.260
You're playing Li Huiniang. Your singing

00:33:16.260 --> 00:33:17.100
doesn't really fit...

00:33:24.940 --> 00:33:26.940
You're keeping your cool pretty well.

00:33:26.940 --> 00:33:27.780
What's wrong?

00:33:28.740 --> 00:33:30.380
Did you know Master Gu was leaving?

00:33:31.780 --> 00:33:33.020
Why didn't you tell me?

00:33:33.420 --> 00:33:34.580
Master wouldn't let me.

00:33:35.540 --> 00:33:37.260
He said no, so you kept it from me?

00:33:37.260 --> 00:33:38.260
I didn't do what you

00:33:38.260 --> 00:33:39.340
told me not to do either.

00:33:41.380 --> 00:33:42.580
I can understand him.

00:33:42.900 --> 00:33:44.100
If I ever have to leave one day,

00:33:44.100 --> 00:33:45.380
I would do the same thing.

00:33:45.410 --> 00:33:46.260
You're leaving?

00:33:46.260 --> 00:33:47.340
Where are you going?

00:33:48.100 --> 00:33:48.980
Now that he's left,

00:33:48.980 --> 00:33:51.140
no one in the troupe will speak for you.

00:33:51.140 --> 00:33:51.980
The whole morning,

00:33:51.990 --> 00:33:53.620
Director Feng didn't even look at you.

00:33:53.620 --> 00:33:55.580
Just do good deeds and
don't ask about the future.

00:33:55.660 --> 00:33:56.660
That's what Master said.

00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:00.940
Stop following me.

00:34:01.220 --> 00:34:02.140
I'm going to the restroom.

00:34:07.220 --> 00:34:08.980
What a total dummy!

00:34:09.860 --> 00:34:11.340
You dare play

00:34:11.340 --> 00:34:12.580
against me?

00:34:12.940 --> 00:34:15.460
I'm undefeated in the
entire Qinqiang opera circle.

00:34:16.540 --> 00:34:17.940
Let's test that out then.

00:34:18.540 --> 00:34:21.300
I'm the best player among the families.

00:34:21.740 --> 00:34:23.580
Beat me before you claim that.

00:34:23.580 --> 00:34:24.740
- Come on.
- Go easy on me.

00:34:24.740 --> 00:34:25.980
What are you doing here?

00:34:26.580 --> 00:34:27.420
Uncle.

00:34:28.660 --> 00:34:29.940
I'm watching Qin'e rehearse.

00:34:30.300 --> 00:34:31.180
No need.

00:34:31.180 --> 00:34:32.100
Just leave.

00:34:32.100 --> 00:34:33.300
We're playing the game.

00:34:33.300 --> 00:34:34.580
I'll play with you later.

00:34:34.940 --> 00:34:36.740
Stop wandering in and out

00:34:36.740 --> 00:34:37.620
and talking big.

00:34:37.620 --> 00:34:38.620
You'll distract Qin'e.

00:34:38.620 --> 00:34:39.490
Get going.

00:34:39.500 --> 00:34:40.940
Troupe Leader Shan, going out?

00:34:42.300 --> 00:34:43.460
- Liu?
- Yes.

00:34:43.540 --> 00:34:44.700
Why are you here?

00:34:44.740 --> 00:34:46.100
To see Qin'e?

00:34:47.740 --> 00:34:49.940
Come sit in my office for a bit.

00:34:49.940 --> 00:34:50.900
No, no, Troupe Leader.

00:34:51.340 --> 00:34:52.460
I'm keeping an eye on the gate.

00:34:52.900 --> 00:34:56.260
With me here, the
provincial troupe is safe!

00:34:56.300 --> 00:34:57.140
Rest assured!

00:34:57.660 --> 00:34:59.140
You're pretty funny.

00:35:01.780 --> 00:35:02.620
Right.

00:35:03.300 --> 00:35:05.700
This is Hu Sanyuan,

00:35:05.820 --> 00:35:06.820
Yi Qin'e's uncle.

00:35:07.340 --> 00:35:08.180
Real uncle.

00:35:08.660 --> 00:35:09.820
Hello, Troupe Leader.

00:35:09.820 --> 00:35:10.700
Thank you.

00:35:10.700 --> 00:35:12.060
Thank you for training Qin'e

00:35:12.060 --> 00:35:13.740
into a Qinqiang opera talent.

00:35:13.740 --> 00:35:14.780
You flatter me.

00:35:15.340 --> 00:35:17.020
But now that Gu is gone,

00:35:17.020 --> 00:35:17.900
the kid must be

00:35:17.900 --> 00:35:19.380
feeling really upset inside.

00:35:19.740 --> 00:35:21.060
As her family,

00:35:21.140 --> 00:35:23.300
help us talk some sense into her.

00:35:23.300 --> 00:35:24.260
Don't worry.

00:35:25.340 --> 00:35:27.060
It's our duty as family members.

00:35:27.540 --> 00:35:28.900
Leave it to us. No problem.

00:35:30.460 --> 00:35:31.300
Alright.

00:35:31.940 --> 00:35:33.500
I'll leave it to the family members.

00:35:33.500 --> 00:35:34.360
I have a meeting.

00:35:34.380 --> 00:35:35.220
I'll leave.

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.140
Okay, okay.

00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:37.120
Come visit when you're free.

00:35:37.140 --> 00:35:38.300
Take care, sir.

00:35:38.300 --> 00:35:39.380
Alright, alright.

00:35:43.420 --> 00:35:44.500
How come

00:35:44.500 --> 00:35:45.940
he even greeted you?

00:35:46.740 --> 00:35:49.340
Uncle, about Master Gu last time.

00:35:49.620 --> 00:35:50.540
A tiny matter.

00:35:50.540 --> 00:35:51.900
I just helped out.

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:53.860
Listen,

00:35:53.860 --> 00:35:55.740
don't meddle in the opera community.

00:35:55.740 --> 00:35:56.590
Don't cause trouble.

00:35:56.660 --> 00:35:57.780
How is this causing trouble?

00:35:57.780 --> 00:35:58.620
Uncle! Uncle!

00:35:58.940 --> 00:36:00.580
Let's go get some liangpi.

00:36:00.700 --> 00:36:02.620
- Diaojia Village has a new stall!
- Let go!

00:36:02.620 --> 00:36:03.460
Let's go!

00:36:09.780 --> 00:36:11.740
Two bowls of liangpi, miss.

00:36:11.740 --> 00:36:12.580
Coming right up.

00:36:14.020 --> 00:36:15.140
Have a seat, Uncle.

00:36:15.820 --> 00:36:17.180
Authentic Ningzhou flavor!

00:36:17.180 --> 00:36:18.660
The liangpi is amazing!

00:36:18.900 --> 00:36:20.540
And the owner is even prettier.

00:36:21.340 --> 00:36:22.340
What are you playing at?

00:36:22.620 --> 00:36:23.540
Playing at what?

00:36:23.820 --> 00:36:24.660
Idiot.

00:36:29.220 --> 00:36:30.860
Gu really left.

00:36:32.140 --> 00:36:33.260
It's my fault.

00:36:33.940 --> 00:36:35.580
Why did I say that to him?

00:36:35.820 --> 00:36:37.780
If you ask me, it's not your business.

00:36:38.300 --> 00:36:39.860
By the time you got out of prison,

00:36:40.140 --> 00:36:41.580
Laidi was already famous.

00:36:41.580 --> 00:36:42.620
You did nothing.

00:36:43.100 --> 00:36:44.220
I wasn't around back then,

00:36:44.220 --> 00:36:45.820
but there were four seniors around.

00:36:45.820 --> 00:36:46.820
The seniors left,

00:36:46.820 --> 00:36:48.340
and we'll have new ones.

00:36:48.420 --> 00:36:50.900
Is it harder to go from
a nobody to the lead,

00:36:50.900 --> 00:36:52.180
or is it harder now?

00:36:53.140 --> 00:36:55.180
What's meant to be yours will come,

00:36:55.180 --> 00:36:56.980
and if not, worrying won't help.

00:36:57.140 --> 00:36:58.580
True enough.

00:36:58.780 --> 00:37:00.140
Alright, stop nagging.

00:37:00.780 --> 00:37:02.340
Or spend another 200 yuan

00:37:02.340 --> 00:37:04.540
to buy a pig and treat everyone.

00:37:05.340 --> 00:37:08.500
Earlier, you drove Gu away
with your nonsense,

00:37:08.500 --> 00:37:09.940
and now you come here looking all gloomy.

00:37:10.020 --> 00:37:10.860
What for?

00:37:11.340 --> 00:37:12.340
Jinxing my business?

00:37:12.820 --> 00:37:14.020
Go and eat.

00:37:25.940 --> 00:37:26.780
Uncle.

00:37:27.180 --> 00:37:28.060
If you ask me,

00:37:28.900 --> 00:37:30.020
she's right.

00:37:30.940 --> 00:37:32.380
You don't need to worry.

00:37:32.380 --> 00:37:34.260
Besides, I'm here now.

00:37:35.140 --> 00:37:36.900
Don't worry about Qin'e's business.

00:37:37.740 --> 00:37:40.580
Pay more attention to your own.

00:37:40.740 --> 00:37:41.620
Save it.

00:37:45.100 --> 00:37:46.660
You haven't seen anything yet.

00:37:47.700 --> 00:37:50.820
If you ask me, men shouldn't be too proud.

00:37:51.220 --> 00:37:52.420
There's a saying.

00:37:52.620 --> 00:37:54.180
"Persistence wins the girl."

00:37:54.340 --> 00:37:56.980
A thick skin makes you invincible.

00:37:56.980 --> 00:37:57.900
If you want a wife,

00:37:58.780 --> 00:37:59.860
don't be too proud.

00:38:00.740 --> 00:38:02.220
If you like her,

00:38:03.420 --> 00:38:05.420
be proactive.

00:38:05.620 --> 00:38:06.500
Proactive?

00:38:06.500 --> 00:38:07.740
Or shameless like you?

00:38:10.180 --> 00:38:11.540
First, we must

00:38:11.620 --> 00:38:13.030
put in the time, endure the loneliness,

00:38:13.030 --> 00:38:13.890
take the knocks,

00:38:13.900 --> 00:38:15.220
and drop the pride.

00:38:16.380 --> 00:38:17.860
However they react,

00:38:18.220 --> 00:38:21.140
we at least check in morning and night.

00:38:21.140 --> 00:38:22.740
If they slap your left cheek,

00:38:22.740 --> 00:38:24.700
smile and offer the right one.

00:38:24.700 --> 00:38:25.740
Let them keep going.

00:38:27.540 --> 00:38:28.540
Can you do that?

00:38:30.220 --> 00:38:31.060
Uncle,

00:38:31.380 --> 00:38:32.660
you don't understand love.

00:38:33.700 --> 00:38:36.420
When you truly fall for someone,

00:38:36.980 --> 00:38:37.860
you'll get it.

00:38:38.220 --> 00:38:40.140
Look at your disgusting face.

00:38:40.220 --> 00:38:41.780
Hurry up and eat, then get lost.

00:38:50.620 --> 00:38:51.460
Sis.

00:38:51.940 --> 00:38:53.140
So you are Aunt Hua!

00:38:54.180 --> 00:38:55.260
Qin'e talks about you

00:38:55.260 --> 00:38:57.180
all day long.

00:38:58.420 --> 00:38:59.260
Liu Hongbing.

00:39:00.340 --> 00:39:01.580
Careful, it's greasy!

00:39:02.620 --> 00:39:03.460
Listen,

00:39:03.780 --> 00:39:05.220
Uncle Sanyuan, my uncle.

00:39:05.620 --> 00:39:07.220
I'll leave him to you from now on.

00:39:07.340 --> 00:39:08.300
Thanks for the trouble.

00:39:08.300 --> 00:39:10.700
Qin'e's business is my business, right?

00:39:10.700 --> 00:39:12.020
Just tell me if you need anything.

00:39:12.020 --> 00:39:12.900
We can work it out.

00:39:13.580 --> 00:39:14.420
Bye, Aunt Hua.

00:39:20.620 --> 00:39:21.820
Is the kid doing okay?

00:39:22.180 --> 00:39:23.020
He's sick.

00:39:25.140 --> 00:39:26.060
Don't worry.

00:39:27.180 --> 00:39:28.620
She'll definitely pull through.

00:39:28.700 --> 00:39:29.580
When it comes

00:39:29.780 --> 00:39:31.540
to this, women are much stronger than men.

00:39:31.540 --> 00:39:33.220
I saw her Troupe Leader.

00:39:33.380 --> 00:39:34.300
I know him.

00:39:34.580 --> 00:39:36.460
We performed together before.

00:39:36.740 --> 00:39:37.900
I played drums for him.

00:39:38.220 --> 00:39:39.660
But he didn't recognize me.

00:39:39.700 --> 00:39:40.540
So I said nothing.

00:39:41.380 --> 00:39:42.340
Why didn't you?

00:39:42.500 --> 00:39:43.460
If I did,

00:39:44.020 --> 00:39:45.420
it'd look like social climbing.

00:39:47.220 --> 00:39:49.260
Better save it for a crucial moment.

00:39:50.140 --> 00:39:52.020
Use it when it really counts.

00:39:53.500 --> 00:39:58.460
(Diaojia Village)

00:40:02.980 --> 00:40:03.820
Uncle.

00:40:04.560 --> 00:40:05.420
Here.

00:40:05.460 --> 00:40:06.300
What?

00:40:06.700 --> 00:40:08.540
Just take it when I tell you to.

00:40:09.580 --> 00:40:10.420
Take it.

00:40:10.780 --> 00:40:11.660
What's this for?

00:40:57.100 --> 00:41:00.540
(Diaojia Village)

00:41:05.900 --> 00:41:06.740
Here.

00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:11.340
Where did you get it?

00:41:13.340 --> 00:41:15.260
The whole village grows flowers.

00:41:15.260 --> 00:41:16.700
You pick them when it's time.

00:41:17.420 --> 00:41:18.260
See you.

00:41:19.260 --> 00:41:20.100
Little brat.

00:41:23.700 --> 00:41:24.700
You can't just pick them!

00:42:05.460 --> 00:42:06.780
Who picked my flower?

00:42:11.540 --> 00:42:12.380
Here.

00:42:17.780 --> 00:42:18.620
How is it?

00:42:19.010 --> 00:42:19.850
Good, right?

00:42:20.900 --> 00:42:21.740
Perfect.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.080 --> 00:43:10.040
On behalf of Qin'e,

00:43:10.040 --> 00:43:12.480
I brought you a small token of appreciation.

00:43:12.480 --> 00:43:15.000
He's an artist. Too lofty and principled.

00:43:15.560 --> 00:43:17.760
You know why Gong Lili
has never been replaced?

00:43:17.880 --> 00:43:19.000
Because she and Director Feng

00:43:19.000 --> 00:43:21.360
both studied under Ms. Li,
the Qinqiang opera maestro.

00:43:25.080 --> 00:43:27.400
Ms. Li, please give us your thoughts.

00:43:27.720 --> 00:43:29.200
Bring that girl who

00:43:29.680 --> 00:43:31.560
performed the fire breathing and Woyu

00:43:31.560 --> 00:43:32.560
up here.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪